room_title: Escape room "The Big Score" by Project Escape in King of Prussia
room_description:
You have been recruited by the infamous and renowned theft ring, the Shrouded Hand, and tasked with stealing one of the most famous diamonds in the world, the Millennium Diamond!
Break in, steal the diamond, then get out! Be quick though, you only have an hour before The Viper and his goons get back!
